Package de.szut.simNil.binaryMaple.avl

Class AVLNode<T extends Comparable<T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.szut.simNil.binaryMaple.AbstractNode<T>
      • de.szut.simNil.binaryMaple.BNode<T>
        • de.szut.simNil.binaryMaple.avl.AVLNode<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - type parameter of node values (for example Integer or String)
    public class AVLNode<T extends Comparable<T>>
extends BNode<T>
    This class extends BNode and is used in AVL trees. In addition to the functionality of BNode, every node of this class keeps track of the height of its left and right subtree. This information is relevant for rebalancing.
    Author:
    Simon Bullik, Nils Malte Kiele
